      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-07/sony-raises-full-year-outlook-after-earnings-beat-estimates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于音乐和游戏软件部门本季度表现优异，索尼集团公司上调了截至 3 月份的财年收入和利润预测。]]></description>
